---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Venture — Traction & Roadmap">
  <section class="section">
    <p class="kicker">Updates</p>
    <h1 class="h1">Pilots and Roadmap</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      We are preparing classroom pilots and collecting educator feedback to improve the kit and resources.
      This page shares current traction, a nine month plan, and how Venture Devils support accelerates our work.
    </p>

    <div class="hr"></div>

    <!-- Traction summary -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="h2">Traction</h2>
      <ul class="dot-list">
        <li>• Early interest from local educators and STEM clubs, first sales on Etsy, and pilot conversations in progress.</li>
        <li>• DNA Assembly Kit iterated with classroom feedback, focus on snap fit accuracy and fast lesson setup.</li>
        <li>• Teacher materials drafted, including quick start cards, worksheets, and answer keys.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="hr"></div>

    <!-- Timeline: horizontal on desktop, vertical on mobile -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="h2">Nine month roadmap</h2>
      <div class="timeline">
        <ol class="timeline-steps">
          <li class="step">
            <div class="dot"></div>
            <p class="step-title">Months 1–2</p>
            <p class="step-body">Finalize kit revisions, confirm pilot partners, prepare teacher packets, and establish survey templates.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="step">
            <div class="dot"></div>
            <p class="step-title">Months 3–4</p>
            <p class="step-body">Run pilots, measure outcomes and timing, collect feedback, and refine parts for durability and cleanup.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="step">
            <div class="dot"></div>
            <p class="step-title">Months 5–6</p>
            <p class="step-body">Publish downloadable teacher materials, package components, and set up quotes and simple ordering.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="step">
            <div class="dot"></div>
            <p class="step-title">Months 7–9</p>
            <p class="step-body">Scale pilots, launch educator community, open broader ordering, and begin outreach to additional districts.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="hr"></div>

    <!-- Grant impact -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="h2">How Venture Devils funding helps</h2>
      <ul class="dot-list">
        <li>• Equipment and materials, printers and filament recycler to support a closed loop process and consistent parts.</li>
        <li>• Curriculum development, printable guides and worksheets, simple video walkthroughs.</li>
        <li>• Pilot support, supplies for classroom runs and data collection.</li>
        <li>• Light marketing and operations, packaging, shipping supplies, and educator outreach.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="hr"></div>

    <!-- Goals -->
    <section class="grid-2">
      <div>
        <h2 class="h2">Near term goals</h2>
        <ul class="dot-list">
          <li>• Deploy pilot kits to partner classrooms and STEM clubs.</li>
          <li>• Measure learning outcomes and activity timing.</li>
          <li>• Refine lesson plans and answer keys from teacher input.</li>
          <li>• Stress test components for durability and easier cleanup.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="h2">What is next</h2>
        <ul class="dot-list">
          <li>• Publish downloadable teacher materials.</li>
          <li>• Set up online ordering and managed fulfillment.</li>
          <li>• Open educator community for tips and variations.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="hr"></div>

    <!-- Card CTA (reuses .cta-band styles in global.css) -->
    <section>
      <div class="cta-band">
        <div class="cta-title">Partner with our pilot program</div>
        <p class="cta-subtext">Interested in hosting a classroom pilot or reviewing materials, we would love to work with you.</p>
        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a class="btn-primary" href="/contact">Request a pilot</a>
          <a class="btn-link" href="/product">See the DNA kit</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
/* Timeline styles scoped to this page */
.timeline { position: relative; margin-top: .75rem; }
.timeline-steps {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  counter-reset: step;
  padding: 0;
  list-style: none;
  margin: 0;
}
.step { position: relative; padding-left: 0; }
.step .step-title { font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 .15rem; color: rgb(30,64,175); }
.step .step-body { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

/* horizontal line behind dots, desktop only */
@media (min-width: 860px) {
  .timeline-steps {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .timeline-steps::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; right: 0;
    top: 22px;
    height: 2px;
    background: rgba(31,75,184,.18);
  }
  .step { padding-top: 1.75rem; }
}

/* dot for each step */
.dot {
  width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 9999px;
  background: rgb(var(--color-mint-400));
  border: 2px solid rgb(31,75,184);
  position: relative;
  margin-bottom: .35rem;
}
@media (min-width: 860px) {
  .step { text-align: left; }
  .dot { margin-bottom: .5rem; }
}

/* on small screens the line becomes vertical for each item */
@media (max-width: 859px) {
  .step { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 14px 1fr; column-gap: .6rem; align-items: start; }
  .dot { grid-row: 1 / span 2; margin-top: .35rem; }
}
</style>

